movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Boring
review: With some redeeming qualities and an overall solid introduction to the saga, The Phantom Menace is watchable, but it is a chore doing so.

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode IX - The Rise of Skywalker
title: Incredible ending
review: What a beautiful film. Incredible ending to the best film franchise of all time. Honestly I'm speechless.

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones
title: Intriguing plot, poor screenplay.
review: Unfortunately, Attack Of The Clones could've been a great movie if it weren't for bad acting and poor screenplay. Many parts are great, but they are overshadowed by a love story that is cringeworthy and creepy.
